headline: Interactive Brokers Expands TipRanks Tools for Its Investors
summary: Interactive Brokers, an automated global electronic broker is deepening its engagement with TipRanks to better serve its customers. IBKR will be integrating a vast suite of TipRanks data sets, information on single stocks and ETFs, and many other idea-generating tools.
